welcome_message_body: Welcome to Sydney, a city known for its stunning harbor, iconic landmarks, and vibrant culture. Get ready to explore and immerse yourself in all the charm this beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The largest and busiest terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The main domestic terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A smaller domestic terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, mainly used by Qantas and its subsidiaries.

terminals.name: Terminal 4
terminals.description: The newest terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving low-cost carriers and regional flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for up to 2 hours per day.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sydney Bankstown Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Sydney Bankstown Airport handles freight and logistics operations.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport terminal.
